{"id": 1320, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些服务也需要一套公开互评体系？", "description": "中差评是很严重的事，大家都要好好表现啊！（题图来自：Laura Liedo）", "record_count": 3240, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161107170231Duy5VmXYnHixgWKI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-28T03:03:00Z", "options": [{"id": 131584, "content": "甲方乙方互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 179, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 131586, "content": "菜场卖菜阿姨和买菜顾客互评，看看到底哪家菜摊小菜最新鲜待客最周到", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 137732, "content": "甲方乙方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843001}, {"id": 137737, "content": "在学校食堂吃饭，对饭菜的评价\n在商店买东西收银员的服务态度评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849970}, {"id": 137489, "content": "买家和护肤品BA的互评，叫你还乱给我推荐产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821703}, {"id": 137745, "content": "给自己工作的单位互评啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707172}, {"id": 137490, "content": "姗姗来迟的外卖小哥和饿瘪的你互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 137491, "content": "老师跟学生评评", "image": null, "praise_count": 147, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848650}, {"id": 137492, "content": "专门水课的学生和大学教授?", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 137494, "content": "军训教官与学生。吼毛吼啊你（微笑）", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 137495, "content": "分手的ex互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843154}, {"id": 137497, "content": "法官与原告被告的互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 137498, "content": "希拉里和川普", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654847}, {"id": 141595, "content": "理发店", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814636}, {"id": 137505, "content": "房东和租户互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 321, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304619}, {"id": 137509, "content": "爸妈和我做得饭菜口味互评！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283795}, {"id": 137510, "content": "政府的通知和我们民众观点", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847897}, {"id": 284454, "content": "通过互相评价想解决什么问题？\r\n基本应该是信息不对称导致的决策失误，所以一切可选择的事物都应该有评价和被评价的权利，以便让后来人进行更好的选择", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359385}, {"id": 137511, "content": "租房", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729840}, {"id": 137768, "content": "饭堂阿姨与我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797439}, {"id": 137513, "content": "好", "image": "img/option/option/20161128114126QqoOIR4ygm9ujd7U.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729840}, {"id": 137514, "content": "同一宿舍的舍友互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848629}, {"id": 137515, "content": "面试官和面试者的互评?", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415308}, {"id": 137773, "content": "像医生和病患，银行窗口和客户，单位窗口和办事人，类似的关系真的会因为评价好坏能改善什么吗？想想自己在窗口的情景，真给个差评，估计接下来要办事就更难了，本身就是‘’约等于‘’的关系，又何必用表面文章来装饰呢？任何权力职能末端的这种‘’微权力‘’只能靠权力上层自己去改善，百姓无能为力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849781}, {"id": 137519, "content": "没人说政府和事业机关单位办事的服务吗，这才是最需要有公开评价体系的", "image": null, "praise_count": 627, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683706}, {"id": 137521, "content": "狗咬狗的时候，需要判别哪只狗更像狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826756}, {"id": 137522, "content": "我和你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635674}, {"id": 137523, "content": "同事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 137779, "content": "火车站售票人员啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283665}, {"id": 137524, "content": "当然是政府事业单位公开办事系统，涉及民生啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836215}, {"id": 137781, "content": "丢东西的大学生和当地警察的互评啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850413}, {"id": 137527, "content": "还是希望大家多一些包容，黑镜的世界真的很恐怖", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055049}, {"id": 137529, "content": "火车，飞机，高铁乘客互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 587861}, {"id": 137530, "content": "那岂不是和黑镜一样？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176256}, {"id": 137531, "content": "快递员快递公司与我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 477791}, {"id": 137791, "content": "老师与学生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839587}, {"id": 139584, "content": "看完电影 对邻座的评价 是爱吧唧吧唧的吃零食 还是后座的那位爱踢凳子 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 426356}, {"id": 137537, "content": "滴滴快车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750435}, {"id": 140609, "content": "甲方乙方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 858266}, {"id": 137539, "content": "我和前男（女）友互评", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567865}, {"id": 137795, "content": "政府", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829676}, {"id": 137542, "content": "政府服务机构和老百姓", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467305}, {"id": 137546, "content": "老爸和老妈，别吵架啦，来互评嘛~", "image": "img/option/option/20161128145323s6WgN0dokVvm2qU7.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491236}, {"id": 137547, "content": "乘客与公交司机互评（司机你不知道我们都要上天了吗！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750425}, {"id": 137549, "content": "好奇心日报：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154585}, {"id": 137550, "content": "约炮对像的功夫", "image": null, "praise_count": 335, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 137551, "content": "服务卫生标准需要互评、监督。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807504}, {"id": 139347, "content": "中国服务", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829556}, {"id": 137556, "content": "雾霾和孩子互评！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 848950}, {"id": 137812, "content": "业主和物业", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 850724}]}